it.unipr.sowide.actodes.actor
Provides classes and interfaces defining the components that must be used, extended or implemented for the development of new kinds of actors.
it.unipr.sowide.actodes.actor.active
Provides classes defining the components driving the execution of active actors.
it.unipr.sowide.actodes.actor.passive
Provides classes defining the components driving the execution of passive actors.
it.unipr.sowide.actodes.configuration
Provides classes defining the components for defining the initial configuration of an actor space.
it.unipr.sowide.actodes.controller
Provides classes and interfaces defining the main components that drive the execution of an actor space.
it.unipr.sowide.actodes.distribution
Provides classes and interfaces defining the components for enabling the communication between the actor spaces of an application.
it.unipr.sowide.actodes.distribution.activemq
Provides classes defining the components supporting the communication between some actor spaces with the ActiveMQ JMS technology.
it.unipr.sowide.actodes.distribution.content
Provides classes defining the message contents used for notifying the network management events.
it.unipr.sowide.actodes.distribution.jeromq
Provides classes defining the components supporting the communication between some actor spaces with the JeroMQ technology.
it.unipr.sowide.actodes.distribution.mina
Provides classes defining the components supporting the communication between some actor spaces with the Apache MINA technology.
it.unipr.sowide.actodes.distribution.rmi
Provides classes defining the components supporting the communication between some actor spaces with the RMI technology.
it.unipr.sowide.actodes.error
Provides classes for the management of errors during the configuration and execution of an actor space.
it.unipr.sowide.actodes.examples.broadcasting
Shows how actors can interact through the use of broadcast messages.
it.unipr.sowide.actodes.examples.buffer
Shows how actors can implement the classical bounded buffer example through an implementation based on behavior change and one based on state change.
it.unipr.sowide.actodes.examples.fibonacci
Shows how actors can create other actors and exchange messages among them by implementing an algorithm for the generation of the Fibonacci numbers.
it.unipr.sowide.actodes.examples.messaging
Shows how actors can exchange messages and how actors can create other actors in remote actor spaces if its execution involves several actors spaces.
it.unipr.sowide.actodes.examples.mobile
Shows how actors can move between different actor spaces.
it.unipr.sowide.actodes.examples.naming
Shows how the naming service can be used for synchronizing some actors.
it.unipr.sowide.actodes.examples.persistence
Shows the use of an actor executor that can store/load inactive actors to/from a persistent storage through a simple master - workers application.
it.unipr.sowide.actodes.examples.pubsub
Shows how to use the topic-based publish and subscribe service by creating a set of actors acting as temperature sensors and another set of actors processing the information coming from the sensors.
it.unipr.sowide.actodes.examples.simulation
Shows a simulation of the classical dining philosophers concurrency problem.
it.unipr.sowide.actodes.examples.unreliability
Shows how to use future messages with timeouts for managing unreliable communication between actors.
it.unipr.sowide.actodes.executor
Provides classes implementing the different behaviors that can be used for managing the execution of the other actors (excluding the other special actor, i.e., the service provider) of the actor space.
it.unipr.sowide.actodes.executor.active
Provides classes defining the executor actors that coordinate the execution of active actors.
it.unipr.sowide.actodes.executor.passive
Provides classes defining the executor actors that drive the execution of passive actors.
it.unipr.sowide.actodes.filtering
Provides classes and interfaces defining patterns and matchers and some useful implementations used for filtering objects.
it.unipr.sowide.actodes.filtering.constraint
Provides classes and interfaces defining constraints and some useful implementations used for filtering objects.
it.unipr.sowide.actodes.interaction
Provides classes and interfaces defining some message contents used in the basic interactions between actors.
it.unipr.sowide.actodes.provider
Provides classes defining the service provider actor.
it.unipr.sowide.actodes.registry
Provides classes and interfaces defining the components for managing the bindings between actors and references and for supporting the exchange of messages between the actors of an application.
it.unipr.sowide.actodes.service
Provides classes defining the services that can be provided by an actor space service provider.
it.unipr.sowide.actodes.service.creation
Provides classes and interfaces defining the creation service.
it.unipr.sowide.actodes.service.group
Provides classes and interfaces defining the group management service and the message contents used for requiring its execution.
it.unipr.sowide.actodes.service.group.content

it.unipr.sowide.actodes.service.logging
Provides classes defining the components of the logging service.
it.unipr.sowide.actodes.service.logging.content
Provides classes defining the message contents used for notifying the logging events.
it.unipr.sowide.actodes.service.mobile
Provides classes and interfaces defining the mobility service and the message contents used for requiring its execution.
it.unipr.sowide.actodes.service.mobile.content
Provides classes defining the message contents used for interacting with the mobile service.
it.unipr.sowide.actodes.service.naming
Provides classes and interfaces defining the naming service and the message contents used for requiring its execution.
it.unipr.sowide.actodes.service.naming.content
Provides classes defining the message contents used for interacting with the naming service.
it.unipr.sowide.actodes.service.persistence
Provides classes and interfaces defining the components for managing a persistent storage for actors an actor-based applications.
it.unipr.sowide.actodes.util.logging
